# Cloudflare Pages Redirects Configuration
# Enforce canonical URLs with trailing slashes for SEO

/home / 301
/news /blog/ 301
/news/ /blog/ 301
/resources /docs/intro/ 301

/:slug /:slug/ 301

# Domain-specific redirects (only work on production domain)
https://ride-more.org https://ride-more.org/ 301
https://www.ride-more.org https://ride-more.org/ 301
